    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable ride that fits your budget? This car is in honest, fair condition and is ready to get you where you need to go! While it shows some typical signs of use and character from its time on the road, it remains a solid and reliable choice for anyone needing a practical daily driver. It's a great opportunity to own a functional vehicle at a fantastic price!",
