    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy. The engine has a severe knock and the transmission struggles to engage, making it unreliable for daily use. Physically, the car has major rust spots, a cracked windshield, and the interior upholstery is heavily torn. It is being sold strictly as-is, ideally for someone looking for a major project or a source for parts.",
